---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Content Platform Case Study | OpsHQ Digital"
  description="Automated content platform with 35+ posts, AI publishing pipeline & page-one Google rankings — at a fraction of previous hosting costs."
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="bg-navy-950 text-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16 md:py-24">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <!-- Text side -->
        <div>
          <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-teal-400 bg-teal-400/10 px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Web & Content</span>
          <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold leading-tight mt-4 mb-6">From Expensive WordPress to Page-One Rankings</h1>
          <p class="text-lg text-slate-300 mb-8">How an automated content platform replaced a $100+/month WordPress setup — and started ranking on Google in under 6 weeks.</p>
          <a href="/contact/?service=web" class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-4 bg-blue-500 text-white font-medium rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-600 transition-colors text-lg">
            Request a Free Discovery Call →
          </a>
        </div>
        <!-- Image side -->
        <div class="relative">
          <img src="/images/hero-casestudy2.jpg" alt="Content platform with automated publishing pipeline, SEO analytics, and page-one Google rankings" class="rounded-2xl shadow-2xl shadow-blue-500/10 w-full" />
          <div class="absolute -inset-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500/20 to-teal-500/20 rounded-2xl blur-xl -z-10"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Challenge -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-4">
        <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-blue-500 rounded-full"></div>
        <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-blue-500 uppercase tracking-wider">The Challenge</span>
      </div>
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-navy-950 mb-6">The Challenge</h2>
      <div class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed space-y-4">
        <p>A content-focused business needed to establish authority across multiple topics. The traditional approach — hire writers, manually publish, cross-post to social media — was too slow and too expensive for a bootstrapped operation running on WordPress with a $100+/month hosting bill and minimal traffic.</p>
        <p>They needed a system that could produce high-quality, SEO-optimized content at scale, distribute it automatically, and measure what was working — without a marketing team.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Solution -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-slate-50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2 mb-4">
        <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-blue-500 rounded-full"></div>
        <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-blue-500 uppercase tracking-wider">What We Built</span>
      </div>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-navy-950 mb-12 text-center">What We Built</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-200">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-navy-950 mb-3">📰 Modern Content Platform</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">A blog built on Astro and MDX with multi-category support, multiple author profiles, and a structured content model. Each post includes SEO metadata, schema markup, and internal linking — all generated automatically.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-200">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-navy-950 mb-3">🤖 AI Content Pipeline</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">Automated blog post generation with SEO optimization — keyword targeting, proper heading structure, internal linking, and meta descriptions. Long-form content optimized for both readers and search engines.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-200">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-navy-950 mb-3">📱 Social Media Distribution</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">Automated cross-posting templates for multiple social platforms, each tailored to the platform's format and audience expectations.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-200">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-navy-950 mb-3">📊 Analytics Dashboard</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">Custom admin portal integrating search analytics, traffic data, and content performance into a single view.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Results -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2 mb-4">
        <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-blue-500 rounded-full"></div>
        <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-blue-500 uppercase tracking-wider">Results</span>
      </div>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-navy-950 mb-12 text-center">The Results</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-slate-100 rounded-xl p-6 text-center">
          <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-blue-500">$100+ → $$$</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mt-2">Hosting cost reduced dramatically</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-slate-100 rounded-xl p-6 text-center">
          <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-blue-500">35+</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mt-2">Posts published</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-slate-100 rounded-xl p-6 text-center">
          <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-blue-500">Page 1</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mt-2">Google rankings in &lt;6 weeks</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-slate-100 rounded-xl p-6 text-center">
          <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-blue-500">80+</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mt-2">Internal cross-links</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-slate-100 rounded-xl p-6 text-center">
          <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-blue-500">95+</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mt-2">PageSpeed score</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-slate-100 rounded-xl p-6 text-center">
          <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-blue-500">Auto</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mt-2">Social distribution</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Tech Stack -->
  <section class="py-12 bg-slate-50">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-wider mb-4 text-center">Technology Used</h3>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-2">
        {['Astro', 'Tailwind CSS', 'MDX', 'Azure', 'Cloudflare', 'GA4', 'Search Console', 'Microsoft Clarity'].map(tech => (
          <span class="text-xs bg-white text-slate-600 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full border border-slate-200">{tech}</span>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Trust + Links -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 italic mb-8">References available on request.</p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4 text-sm">
        <a href="/services/web/" class="text-blue-500 hover:text-blue-600 font-medium transition-colors">See our web development services →</a>
        <a href="/services/cloud/" class="text-blue-500 hover:text-blue-600 font-medium transition-colors">See our cloud services →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-navy-950 to-navy-800 text-white py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Ready to Build Your Own Content Engine?</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-300 mb-8">Every project starts with a free discovery call. Tell us what you're trying to accomplish.</p>
      <a href="/contact/?service=web" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 bg-blue-500 text-white font-medium rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-600 transition-colors min-h-[44px] text-lg">
        Request a Discovery Call
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
  <Fragment slot="head">
    <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
      "@context": "https://schema.org",
      "@graph": [
        {
          "@type": "BreadcrumbList",
          "itemListElement": [
            { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 1, "name": "Home", "item": "https://opshqdigital.com/" },
            { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 2, "name": "Our Work", "item": "https://opshqdigital.com/work/" },
            { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 3, "name": "Content Platform Case Study", "item": "https://opshqdigital.com/work/content-platform/" }
          ]
        },
        {
          "@type": "Article",
          "headline": "From Expensive WordPress to Page-One Rankings",
          "description": "Automated content platform with 35+ posts, AI publishing pipeline & page-one Google rankings — at a fraction of previous hosting costs.",
          "url": "https://opshqdigital.com/work/content-platform/",
          "author": { "@type": "Organization", "name": "OpsHQ Digital", "@id": "https://opshqdigital.com/#organization" },
          "publisher": { "@type": "Organization", "name": "OpsHQ Digital", "@id": "https://opshqdigital.com/#organization" },
          "mainEntityOfPage": "https://opshqdigital.com/work/content-platform/"
        }
      ]
    })} />
  </Fragment>
</BaseLayout>
